  <fileinfo>
    <info_history><![CDATA[
5/21/2014 - Tim Shadow
-Removed the source id's from: xDisEidite, xDisManaFv, xDisWstTmb. 
    
    
Disease text structure -

Called via the proceedure DiseaseTxt (proceedure is in the community proceedures files).

disName: name of the disease
  
-disease catagory -
DiseaseCat.Contact 
DiseaseCat.Ingested 
DiseaseCat.Inhaled
DiseaseCat.Injury

- save type - 
DiseaseSave.Fort
DiseaseSave.Ref
DiseaseSave.Will
abValue4 - fixed DC

StandardDC used for calculating DCs if they aren't fixed.

- onset -
abValue d abValue2
DisOnset.Day
DisOnset.Immediate
DisOnset.Override
  disOnset: disease onset text

- frequency -
abDuration
DisFreq.PerDay
DisFreq.PerWeek
DisOnset.Override
  disFreq: disease frequency text

- effect -
disEffect: disease effect text  

- saves -
abValue3  
DisSave.Override
  disSaves: disease save text

- extra text -
disExtra: any extra text]]></info_history>
    <info_todo><![CDATA[The Adjustment to add a disease doesn't quite work yet. Need to figure out how to make a single adjustment adjust two things.  In this case, the disease and the weapon it is on.]]></info_todo>
    </fileinfo>
  <thing id="pCBDisease" name="Disease" description="Gives creature the specified disease on a weapon.\n\nSpecify the name of the weapon in the source field." compset="InPlay">
    <fieldval field="pWhat" value="Weapon"/>
    <usesource source="srcS2Adjus"/>
    <tag group="ProductId" tag="HLCommunit"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="NoPathSoc"/>
    <tag group="Adjustment" tag="S2Custom"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="NoIncr"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="AdjNoPlus"/>
    <tag group="OthAdjCat" tag="Race"/>
    <bootstrap thing="xxCBDisHel"></bootstrap>
    <eval phase="PreLevel" priority="5000" index="2"><![CDATA[
      ~ If we're not enabled, get out now
      doneif (field[pIsOn].value <> 1)
      ~ If nothing chosen, get out now
      doneif (field[pChosen].ischosen <> 1)

      ~ reveal chosen disease

      ~debug field[pChosen].chosen.idstring

      var chsn as string
      chsn = field[pChosen].chosen.idstring
      chsn = "thingid." & chsn


      foreach pick in hero from RaceAbil where chsn
         perform eachpick.delete[Hide.Special]
         perform eachpick.delete[Helper.SpcDisable]
      nexteach]]></eval>
    <eval phase="PreLevel" priority="11000"><![CDATA[
      ~ All things
      field[pUsePicks].value = 0

      field[pCandExpr].text = "component.RaceAbil & Ailment.Disease & !Helper.Helper"

      ~ field[pCandExpr].text = "Ailment.Disease"]]></eval>
    </thing>
